  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 63-1-35, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REQUIRE THE COMMISSIONER OF PUBLIC SAFETY TO ISSUE A NEW, RENEWAL OR DUPLICATE DRIVER'S LICENSE, TEMPORARY DRIVING PERMIT OR COMMERCIAL DRIVER'S LICENSE TO ANY LICENSED FIREARM HOLDER WHICH STATES THE TYPE OF ENHANCED FIREARM ENDORSEMENT THE LICENSEE OR PERMITTEE POSSESSES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
